<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png+xml" href="assets/favicon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">

</head>

<body class="About-us">


    <header>
        <nav class="container">
            <ul>    

                <li class="nav-home">
                    <a class="button" href="home" data-type="nav home">
                        <img src="assets/logo-ticket+2.png" alt="Logo">
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-search-bar">
                    <form id="search-form" action="/all-events" method="get">

                        <input type="search" id="site-search" name="keyword" placeholder="Search: event, artist, date etc." maxlength="20" aria-label="Search through site content">
                        <button type="submit">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                        </button>
                    </form>                    
                </li>

            </ul>
            <section class="nav-block">

              <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger-closing-button">              <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></button>
            <ul>
                <li class="nav-all-events"><a href="all-events">All Events</a></li>
                <li class="nav-about-us active"><a href="about-us">About Us</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <% if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <li><a href="form" class="button" data-type="nav">Sign In
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                    </a></li>
                <% } %>
                
                <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                    <li><a href="profile" class="button" data-type="nav">Profile
                        <% if (profileImage.startsWith("data:image")) { %>
                          <img src="<%= profileImage %>" alt="Profile picture">
                        <% } else { %>
                          <img src="assets/profile-default.jpg" alt="Default Profile picture">
                        <% } %>
                      </a></li>
                    <% } %>
            </ul>

            </section>

            <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
        </nav>  
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>

            <div class="AboutUsBlok">
                <p>Welcome to Ticket+! Easily discover the most enjoyable events near you, from festivals and concerts
                    to sports matches and theater performances. Add your favorite events to your favorites list and
                    receive personalized recommendations based on your preferences. With Ticket+, you"re always informed
                    about what"s happening and enjoy reliable, up-to-date information. Join our community and never miss
                    an unforgettable experience again.</p>
                <img src="/assets/Logo-ticket+.png" alt="Logo Ticket+">
            </div>

            <h2>FAQ</h2>
            <div class="accordeonPlaatsing">
                <div class="accordeon">
                    <button class="accordion">Are my favorite events private?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                        <p>Indeed, your favorites list is private, and only you have access to this information. We do
                            not share your favorite events with others.</p>
                    </div>

                    <button class="accordion">How can I add an event to my favorites?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                        <p>It"s very simple! When you"re viewing an event, look for the "Add to Favorites" button next
                            to the event information. Click on it, and the event will be added to your favorites list.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <button class="accordion">How often is the events calendar updated?</button>
                    <div class="panel">
                        <p>We begrijpen hoe belangrijk het is om altijd up-to-date te blijven! Daarom streven we ernaar
                            onze evenementenkalender zo snel mogelijk bij te werken zodra nieuwe informatie beschikbaar
                            is. Ons team zet zich in om ervoor te zorgen dat je altijd de meest nauwkeurige en actuele
                            informatie hebt over alle evenementen op Ticket+.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <div class="contact-card">
                <div class="contact-card-image">
                    <img src="/assets/card-default.jpg" alt="Afbeelding">
                </div>
                <div class="contact-card-form">
                    <form>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Name">
                        <input type="email" placeholder="E-mailadress">
                        <textarea placeholder="Message"></textarea>
                        <button type="submit">Send</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <section>
            <div>
                <h2>Find your event</h2>
                <a href="all-events" class="button"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>Search Event</a>
            </div>

            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h6>Navigation</h6>
                </li>
                <li><a href="home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="all-events">All Events</a></li>
                <li><a href="about-us">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="profile">Profile</a></li>
            </ul>

            <div>
                <div>
                    <h6>Contact</h6>
                    <a href="mailto:ticket@ticketplus.com">ticket@ticketplus.com</a>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h6>Based in</h6>
                    <p>Amsterdam, <br> The Netherlands</p>
                </div>

                <address>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        </li>
                        <li><a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
                        </li>
                        <li><a href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i></a></li>
                    </ul>
                </address>
            </div>
        </section>

        <span>Â©2024 by Ticket+</span>
    </footer>


 <script src="hamburger.js"></script>
 <script src="accordion.js"></script>



</body>